<h2 style="color: red; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Summary</h2>
<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
    Alkanes are simple hydrocarbons with relatively low reactivity. They are widely used as fuels due to their exothermic combustion reactions.
</p>


